36 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
37 recognize and commend Kathy Hogan Trocheck, also known worldwide as Mary Kay
38 Andrews, for her many outstanding accomplishments and extend best wishes for continued
39 health and happiness.
40 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
41 to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Kathy Hogan
42 Trocheck.
